%% Mirror of 07-os-metamodel-stack.d2; D2 owns layout/styling, Mermaid owns reviewability.
flowchart TB
  Sources["Sources<br/>official publications, datasets, expert notes"]:::source
  Graph["Canonical graph<br/>sources + entities + edges + views"]:::graph
  Evidence["Evidence ledger<br/>claim, source, status, confidence, review_state"]:::evidence
  Gates["Readiness gates<br/>G1-G8 blockers and approvals"]:::gate
  Views["Views<br/>Lifecycle | Evidence | Control Tower | NPA Lattice"]:::view
  KPI["KPI layer<br/>coverage, gaps, actions, deadlines"]:::kpi
  Decision["Decision cadence<br/>pilot -> scale -> 2030 operating standard"]:::decision
  Caveat["DRAFT / EXPERT REVIEW<br/>Not legal opinion"]:::caveat

  Sources -->|normalize IDs| Graph
  Graph -->|derive claims| Evidence
  Evidence -->|validate readiness| Gates
  Gates -->|select management question| Views
  Views -->|aggregate only reviewed signals| KPI
  KPI -->|quarterly decision loop| Decision
  Evidence -->|governs wording| Caveat
  Decision -->|keeps scope bounded| Caveat

  classDef source fill:#f4f7fb,stroke:#6e7480,color:#111827;
  classDef graph fill:#eaf2ff,stroke:#2563eb,color:#172b55;
  classDef evidence fill:#fff8e6,stroke:#d97706,color:#111827;
  classDef gate fill:#eefaf1,stroke:#2f7d44,color:#111827;
  classDef view fill:#ecfeff,stroke:#0891b2,color:#111827;
  classDef kpi fill:#ffffff,stroke:#d8deea,color:#111827;
  classDef decision fill:#f3f0ff,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#111827;
  classDef caveat fill:#fff1f0,stroke:#b42318,color:#111827;
